extends hwlayout.pug
block content
	h2 Exercise 1: Adjustable Effects
	h3 Sliders and buttons
	p Integrate sliders and buttons from 
		a(href="https://p5js.org/reference/#/libraries/p5.dom" target="_blank") p5.dom library
		|  to enable adjustable effects as in these examples: 
		a(href="/p5/flower-slider" target="_blank") (1)
		|  and 
		a(href="/p5/sound-slider" target="_blank") (2)
		|  .
	p Use the following functions:
	p createSlider(), value(), changed()
	p createButton(), mousePressed()
	p position(), style()

	h2 Exercise 2: Interaction
	h3 Keyboard
	p Use p5.play library. Here is  
		a(href="/p5/play" target="_blank") an example.
	p Use the following functions:
	p createSprite()
	p somesprite.draw = function(){};
	p keydown()
	p position.x, position.y
	p overlap(), collide(), displace()
	p random()
	h2 Exercise 3: Image
	p Use p5.js image functions. Link to 
		a(href="/p5/image" target="_blank") an example.
	p Use the following functions:
	p loadImage()
	p image(), tint(), blend(), filter()
	p get(), set(), updatePixels()